1 (3) (2) Department means the Department of Agriculture;
2 (4) (3) Commercial fertilizer means any formula or product
3 distributed for further distribution or ultimate use as a plant nutrient,
4 intended to promote plant growth, containing one or more plant nutrients
5 recognized by the Association of American Plant Food Control Officials in
6 its official publication. The term commercial fertilizer shall not be
7 deemed to include unmanipulated animal and vegetable manures but shall be
8 deemed to include both finished products and fertilizer ingredients
9 capable of being used in the formulation of a finished product;
10 (5) (4) Bulk means nonpackaged;
11 (6) (5) Custom-blended product means any individually compounded
12 commercial fertilizer or beneficial substance that is soil conditioner
